What is the difference between throw and throws. Write the code
for the same.

Ans-
1.Throw is use on the method whereas
throws is use on the method signature.
2.Throw keyword is use to throw an exception
 explicitly in the code, inside the function or block of
 code.
 where as throws keyword is use to in the method
 signature to declare an exception which might be thrown by
 the function while the execution of the code.

 3.The throw keyword is followed by an instance of Exception.
 whereas he throws keyword is followed by class names of
 Exceptions.